"    </t>\n"
"    <t t-if=\"object.x_studio_users != 0\">\n"
"        <li>用户：<t t-out=\"object.x_studio_users or ''\">2025</t></li>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"    <t t-if=\"object.x_studio_version != False\">\n"
"        <li>版本：<t t-out=\"object.x_studio_version or ''\">18.3</t></li>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"    <t t-if=\"object.x_studio_license_key != False\">\n"
"        <li>授权密钥： <t t-out=\"object.x_studio_license_key or "
